Originally ripped by Terminal Escape, posted on May 25, 2023 Description from Terminal Escape:
 Five blasts of by-the-books DBeat repetition, delivered with every ounce of raw fury the (sub)genre demands. Bands can use more than two riffs if they want...but DISHUMAN makes it clear that the extra riffs aren't really necessary. "Hate For This System" on repeat all damn day. DEMO 2021
